cross: Callianthe Blue Boy x Guarianthe bowringiana

measurements.description:
Fifty-five flowers and one bud on six up to 31-cm upright inflorescences; 38 pseudobulbs, clean foliage,
	plant 71cm tall and 95cm wide, plastic pot 15.5cm tall x 30-cm wide;
	sepal tips slightly recurved, light wisteria blue; petals slightly ruffled, tips recurved,
	darker wisteria blue distally; lip tubular, margin ruffled, intense wisteria blue,
	lighter centrally; column cream, substance firm; texture crystalline; received AM 84
	award# 20225349.
